result.notes: Video transect survey of Maerl and Zostera beds at the mouth of the Percuil River for the St Mawes Harbour Conservation Trust.  Collected to continue the baseline data on maerl and sea grass beds in this area and to promote awareness and interest in life underwater in St Mawes harbour.
